verbose_text: Based on our current observations that fgf3 expression precedes that of tph1a and 5-HT by several hours, and that the nkx2.4b-positive hypothalamic domain is smaller after fgf3 impairment before the appearance of mature serotonergic CSF-c cells, we propose that Fgf3 is critical during early stages when progenitors are still proliferating.
